'''飓风罗莎'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Rosa}}）是相对活跃的[[1994年太平洋飓风季|1994年太平洋飓风季]]中唯一一场曾经[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]的[[太平洋飓风季|太平洋飓风]]，在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]至少夺走四条人命。飓风的残留湿气还于1994年10月在美国[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]引发大面积洪灾，导致22人遇难，经济损失达数亿美元。天气系统最初在10月8日成为热带低气压，但次日又逐渐消退。10月8日，气旋重新形成并在逼近墨西哥期间稳步增强，最终于登陆前不久达到最高强度，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下属二级飓风标准。此外，罗莎还是本季最后一场飓风和倒数第二场热带风暴。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Rosa 1994 track.png}}
10月8日，一片带有[[大气环流|环流]]的扰动天气区发展出[[对流|对流]]，成为第十九{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压<ref name="discussion1">{{cite report | author = Mayfield | date = 1994-10-08 | title = Tropical Depression Nineteen-E Special Discussion 1 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214104/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.001 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.001 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但气象机构起初预测气旋很快会在强烈[[风切变|风切变]]的影响下消散<ref name="TCRp2">{{cite report | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994-prelim/rosa/prelim02.gif | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Rosa | pages = 2 | date = 1994-11-22 | format = GIF | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212234/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994-prelim/rosa/prelim02.gif }}</ref>。低气压的移动幅度很小，并因风切变的持续影响而无法发展<ref name="discussion2">{{cite report | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.002 | author = Mayfield | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183302/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.002 | date = 1994-10-08 | title = Tropical Depression Nineteen-E Discussion Number 2 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。气旋难以有效组织，到10月9日时组织已经非常混乱，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此中止发布公告<ref name="discussion6">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233039/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.006 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.006 | author = Mayfield | date = 1994-10-08 | title = Tropical Depression Nineteen-E Discussion Number 1 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

气旋残留向东移动，同另一片扰动天气区相互影响，令对流再生<ref name="TCRp1">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303203432/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994-prelim/rosa/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994-prelim/rosa/prelim01.gif | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Rosa | pages = 1 | date = 1994-11-22 | format = GIF | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，系统于10月10日再度成为热带低气压，其中可能存在新的环流中心<ref name="discussion7">{{cite report | author = Rappaport | date = 1994-10-10 | title = Tropical Depression Nineteen-E Discussion Number 7 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121022123016/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.007 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.007 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-22 }}</ref>。不过，美国国家飓风中心的初步报告中既未说明气旋一度消散，也没有提及之后的再生<ref name="TCRp3">{{cite report | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Rosa | pages = 1 | date = 1994-11-22 | format = GIF | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220828/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994-prelim/rosa/prelim03.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994-prelim/rosa/prelim03.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。低气压所在海域环境有利于热带气旋发展，同时又基本没有移动<ref name="TCRp1" />，于10月11日升级成热带风暴并获名“罗莎”（{{lang|en|Rosa}}）<ref name="discussion11">{{cite report | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.011 | title = Tropical Storm Rosa Discussion Number 11 | date = 1994-10-11 | author = Rappaport | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121022123108/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.011 | archivedate = 2012-10-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，再于一天后在[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]最南端以南约555公里洋面进一步升级成飓风<ref name="discussion12">{{cite report | date = 1994-10-12 | author = Rappaport | title = Hurricane Rosa Discussion Number 14 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.011 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121022123108/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994/rosa/tropdisc/nep1994.011 | archivedate = 2012-10-22 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | access-date = 2016-09-05 }}</ref>。接下来一天半里罗莎继续缓慢移动，然后在[[低压槽|低压槽]]的影响下加速朝[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]前进。10月14日，飓风达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]160公里，最低[[气压|中心气压]]974[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.76[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下属二级飓风标准。数小时后，罗莎从[[马萨特兰|马萨特兰]]东南偏南方向约110公里处登陆。风暴环流在山区上空迅速减弱，最终于10月15日消散。<ref name="TCRp1" />

== 防灾措施、影响和善后 ==
10月12日，[[库利亚坎|库利亚坎]]至[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]以及[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]][[北纬24度线|北纬24°]]以南的沿海地区收到[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]，同时曼萨尼约至[[特皮克|特皮克]]接获热带风暴警告。10月14日，库利亚坎到科连特斯角（{{lang|en|Cabo Corrientes}}）间沿海地区进入飓风警告生效状态，科连特斯角至曼萨尼约以南地区则收到热带风暴警告。所有观察预警和警告都在当天中止。<ref name="TCRp5">{{cite report | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Rosa | date = 1994-11-22 | author = Lixion Avila | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | pages = 5 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994-prelim/rosa/prelim05.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215022/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994-prelim/rosa/prelim05.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>

[[File:Rosa_1994_rainfall.gif|thumb]]

10月13至14日，“伦敦精神号”（{{lang|en|London Spirit}}）和“玛丽·马士基号”（{{lang|en|Marie Maersk}}）船只在海上分别遭遇热带风暴或飓风强度风力<ref name="TCRp4">{{cite report | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | pages = 4 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994-prelim/rosa/prelim04.gif | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002035024/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1994-prelim/rosa/prelim04.gif | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Rosa | date = 1994-11-22 | author = Lixion Avila | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。其中“玛丽·马士基号”的位置离[[风眼|风眼]]很近，所以观测数据对气象机构很有参考价值<ref name="TCRp2" />。

[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]和[[杜兰戈州|杜兰戈州]]各有一人溺毙，[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]有四人失踪。纳亚里特州有十万余人的住房受损。罗莎产生的狂风导致锡那罗亚州许多[[电线杆|电线杆]]、[[高压电线|电缆]]和房屋受损，山区的降雨量在76到127毫米之间，引发多起[[山崩|山体滑坡]]。<ref name="TCRp2" />[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]发生多起[[泥石流|泥石流]]，两个沿海村庄有约400人被迫疏散<ref name="Daily Herald">{{cite news | page = 3 | date = 1994-10-15 | newspaper = Chicago Daily Herald | title = Mexican West Coast Survives Hurricane | url = http://dailyherald.newspaperarchive.com/daily-herald-suburban-chicago/1994-10-15/ | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | archive-date = 2016-09-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160911134800/http://dailyherald.newspaperarchive.com/daily-herald-suburban-chicago/1994-10-15/ | dead-url = no }}{{subscription}}</ref>。风暴在墨西哥部分沿海和内陆地区降下暴雨，其中梅萨德佩德罗巴勃罗（{{lang|en|Mesa de Pedro Pablo}}）降雨量最高，达358毫米<ref name="HPCRosa">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054556/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/rosa1994.html | deadurl = no | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | author = David M. Roth | title = Hurricane Rosa  - October 9-15, 1994 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/rosa1994.html | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date =  }}</ref>。

气旋还把湿气送入美国境内，这些湿气同[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]北部的水分共同影响，于10月15至19日产生强烈[[雷暴|雷暴]]，[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[得克萨斯州行政区划|38个县]]部分地区发生洪灾。除沿海地区外，[[圣哈辛托河_(德克萨斯州)|圣哈辛托河]]（{{lang|en|San Jacinto River}}）和[[三一河_(德克萨斯州)|三一河]]（{{lang|en|Trinity River}}）盆地周边灾情最为严重，降雨总量最少也有200毫米，最多的超过710毫米。<ref name="USGSp1">{{cite web | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193401/http://pubs.usgs.gov/fs/fs-073-94/pdf/FS-94-073.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://pubs.usgs.gov/fs/fs-073-94/pdf/FS-94-073.pdf | title = Floods in Southeast Texas, October 1994 | publisher = [[美国地质调查局|United States Geological Survey]] | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | date = 1995-01 | pages = 1 }}</ref>受降水影响，有19间气象站测得百年一遇的洪水，多项数据的原有纪录被打破，其中有些是在1940年所创。[[杰克逊县_(德克萨斯州)|杰克逊县]][[埃德娜_(德克萨斯州)|埃德娜]]（{{lang|en|Edna}}）附近的[[拉瓦卡河|拉瓦卡河]]（{{lang|en|Lavaca River}}）水位打破1936年的纪录。<ref name="USGSp2">{{cite web | title = Floods in Southeast Texas, October 1994 | publisher = United States Geological Survey | format = PDF | accessdate = 2016-09-05 | date = 1995-01 | pages = 2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193401/http://pubs.usgs.gov/fs/fs-073-94/pdf/FS-94-073.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://pubs.usgs.gov/fs/fs-073-94/pdf/FS-94-073.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>洪灾导致3069户民宅被毁，另有6560套严重受损，6148套的破坏程度较轻。铁路和公路受到持续破坏，天然气和[[管输工艺|石油管道]]因受损泄露，圣哈辛托河下游和[[加尔维斯顿湾|加尔维斯顿湾]]（{{lang|en|Galveston Bay}}）的环境受到破坏。德克萨斯州东南部因洪灾受到价值七亿美元（1995年美元）的损失，共有22人遇难。<ref name="USGSp1" />10月18日，[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]将受灾最严重的地区划为灾区<ref name="FEMA">{{cite web | publisher = [[联邦紧急事务管理局|Federal Emergency Management Agency]] | accessdate = 2012-03-15 | title = Texas Severe Storm, Thunderstorms, Flooding | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120315134643/http://www.fema.gov/news/event.fema?id=2242 | date = 2005-05-23 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/event.fema?id=2242 | archivedate = 2012-03-15 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。该机构此后一共收到约2万6000份救灾援助申请，批准援助金总额5400万美元<ref name="USGSp1" />。

